{"title":"来吧，兄弟","authors":["荷·莱贝罗"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":5,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔莫桑比克〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷·莱贝罗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我讲讲你的生平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我看看你身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人刀枪留下的伤痕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，请这样讲给我听："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“瞧，我的双手已经变形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们捍卫过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的国家和人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“瞧，我的身上伤疤鳞鳞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在侵略者的淫威面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从未卑躬屈膝，哀求饶命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“瞧，我的嘴上也有刀印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它曾无畏地讴歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的自由和觉醒……”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任华译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}